$ /usr/share/hwdata

`/usr/share/hwdata/pci.ids` lists → hardware/PCI[PCI] IDs. The most actual IDs can be downloaded from → http://pci-ids.ucw.cz/v2.2/pci.ids. Alternatively,
the shell script `update-pciids` can be invoked.

`/usr/share/hwdata/usb.ids` lists → hardware/USB[USB] IDs. The most actual IDs can be downloaded from → http://www.linux-usb.org/usb.ids.

sa:
  → Linux/fhs/usr/share
